Katherine Perry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katherine_Perry 0 Katherine Perry (January 5, 1897 – October 14, 1983) was an American stage and film actress. She appeared in 36 films between 1920 and 1936. Perry also was in the Ziegfeld Follies.She was born in New York City and died in Woodland Hills, Los Angeles. She was the second wife of Owen Moore.
